(1) A unified evaluation framework for four VLMs on Winoground;
(2) a TextSceneGraphParser covering SVO, prepositional, copular, existential, and possessive constructions;
(3) a Graph Asymmetry Scorer via optimal bipartite matching targeting agent–patient role reversal;
(4) systematic caption ablation experiments quantifying entity-identity vs. relational-syntax reliance;
(5) a multi-turn SG filtering strategy achieving group score 66.0, a new open-source state-of-the-art on Winoground.
